<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.3">
<l>paṇaittō ḷiḷavāycci pālpāynta koṅkai</l>
<l>yaṇaittāra vuṇṭu kiṭantavip piḷḷai</l>
<l>yiṇaikkālil veḷḷit taḷainiṉ ṟilaṅkuṅ</l>
<l>kaṇaikkā liruntavā kāṇīrē  kārikai yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ladies, see the way [his] shins shine permanently</l>
<l>with silver anklets on the pair of feet of this child who,</l>
<l>after embracing the milk-gushing breasts of the young cowherdess with bamboo-like arms,</l>
<l>drank, so that he became full, and slept. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
